    <item>
      <title>交易员关注降息路径，欧元飙升至一年高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/euro-surges-to-one-year-high-as-traders-eye-interest-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元兑美元升至一年来最高水平，因为货币交易员押注美国央行行长将在杰克逊霍尔美联储经济研讨会上强调降低借贷成本的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/euro-surges-to-one-year-high-as-traders-eye-interest-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:47:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员对降息押注信心增强，美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/treasuries-gain-as-updated-us-data-fuels-bets-for-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国就业数据修正和美联储最新政策会议纪要强化了人们对下个月开始降息的押注后，美国国债价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/treasuries-gain-as-updated-us-data-fuels-bets-for-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Western Asset 的 Leech 因美国证券交易委员会调查而休假</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/western-asset-s-ken-leech-takes-leave-of-absence-amid-sec-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西方资产管理公司 (Western Asset Management) 联席首席投资官肯·利奇 (Ken Leech) 可能面临美国证券交易委员会的执法行动，该委员会正在调查某些客户在分配衍生品交易的收益和损失时是否比其他客户享有更多利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/western-asset-s-ken-leech-takes-leave-of-absence-amid-sec-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 13:25:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据修正和美联储会议纪要支持利率押注，黄金价格接近历史最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/gold-steadies-near-record-as-markets-wait-for-powell-address</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储会议纪要和美国非农就业数据下调强化了人们对决策者将在9月份降息的预期，黄金交易价格接近历史高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/gold-steadies-near-record-as-markets-wait-for-powell-address</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 01:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美联储 9 月降息已成定局，股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市上涨，债券收益率下跌，美联储最新会议纪要和美国非农就业数据大幅下调，强化了市场对美联储官员将在 9 月份降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 22:36:04 GMT</pubDate>
